# EduTech — EduLens AI

This workspace hosts **EduLens AI**, a structured education product (not a generic chatbot).

## Product modules

- Homework Analyzer (`/edulens/homework-analyzer`)
- Lesson Generator (`/edulens/lesson-generator`)
- Mistake Book (`/edulens/mistake-book`)
- Dashboard (`/edulens/dashboard`)
- Reports (`/edulens/reports/[id]`)

## Architecture rules

- UI must not call LLMs directly — use API routes under `src/app/api/edulens/`
- Business logic lives in `src/lib/edulens/services/edulens-service.ts`
- AI: provider → prompt builder → JSON parser → Zod validator
- Default mode: `EDULENS_AI_MODE=mock` with seeded demo data

## Code conventions

- Code comments and UI strings: English (unless lesson content requires Chinese)
- User-facing answers: match the user's language
- JSDoc for non-obvious functions
- Minimal diffs; reuse existing components under `src/components/edulens/`
